ze:39px}.elementor-widget-heading .elementor-heading-title.elementor-size-xxl{font-size:59px}<\/style><h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">O que \u00e9 Smarketing?\n<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7989f7e e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"7989f7e\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-a3bc282 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"a3bc282\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<style>\/*! elementor - v3.16.0 - 20-09-2023 *\/\n.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-stacked .elementor-drop-cap{background-color:#69727d;color:#fff}.elementor-widget-text-editor.elementor-drop-cap-view-framed .elementor-drop-cap{color:#69727d;border:3px solid;background-color:transparent}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap{margin-top:8px}.elementor-widget-text-editor:not(.elementor-drop-cap-view-default) .elementor-drop-cap-letter{width:1em;height:1em}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap{float:left;text-align:center;line-height:1;font-size:50px}.elementor-widget-text-editor .elementor-drop-cap-letter{display:inline-block}<\/style>\t\t\t\t<p data-reader-unique-id=\"3\">&#8220;Smarketing&#8221; \u00e9 uma jun\u00e7\u00e3o das palavras &#8220;sales&#8221; (vendas) e &#8220;marketing&#8221;. Refere-se \u00e0 integra\u00e7\u00e3o e alinhamento de estrat\u00e9gias e atividades entre os departamentos de marketing e vendas de uma empresa. Essa abordagem visa a harmoniza\u00e7\u00e3o de objetivos, processos, comunica\u00e7\u00e3o e tecnologia entre essas duas equipes, garantindo que trabalhem juntas de maneira sin\u00e9rgica.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-124ee37 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"124ee37\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-decc0c5 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"decc0c5\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-reader-unique-id=\"4\">Para entender melhor o conceito de smarketing, \u00e9 importante considerar que, em muitas empresas, o marketing \u00e9 respons\u00e1vel por atrair leads e criar demanda, enquanto as vendas convertem esses leads em clientes pagantes. No entanto, essa divis\u00e3o de responsabilidades muitas vezes resulta em silos organizacionais, comunica\u00e7\u00e3o ineficiente e falta de compreens\u00e3o m\u00fatua das necessidades e desafios de cada departamento.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-01f3725 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"01f3725\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-f1f426a elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"f1f426a\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-reader-unique-id=\"5\">O smarketing supera essas barreiras, permitindo que o marketing e as vendas trabalhem em estreita colabora\u00e7\u00e3o, compartilhando informa\u00e7\u00f5es, estabelecendo metas conjuntas e avaliando o desempenho em conjunto. Isso n\u00e3o apenas melhora a efici\u00eancia, mas tamb\u00e9m impulsiona os resultados.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-1781574 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"1781574\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b6fd9c0 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"b6fd9c0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Benef\u00edcios do Smarketing: Por que alinhar Marketing e Vendas?\n<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-4d6a1d1 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"4d6a1d1\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-11cc731 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"11cc731\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-reader-unique-id=\"8\"><strong>Melhora a qualidade dos leads:<\/strong><\/p><p data-reader-unique-id=\"9\">Quando marketing e vendas trabalham juntos, \u00e9 mais f\u00e1cil definir crit\u00e9rios claros para leads qualificados. O marketing pode entender melhor as necessidades e expectativas dos vendedores, resultando em leads mais relevantes e de maior qualidade. Isso, por sua vez, acelera o processo de convers\u00e3o e aumenta a taxa de fechamento de vendas.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-439a9eb e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"439a9eb\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-440ffdc elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"440ffdc\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-reader-unique-id=\"10\"><strong>Aumenta a\u00a0efici\u00eancia\u00a0operacional:<\/strong><\/p><p data-reader-unique-id=\"11\">O alinhamento de estrat\u00e9gias e processos reduz a duplica\u00e7\u00e3o de esfor\u00e7os. As equipes de marketing e vendas podem colaborar na cria\u00e7\u00e3o de conte\u00fado, no desenvolvimento de campanhas e no compartilhamento de informa\u00e7\u00f5es sobre os clientes em potencial. Isso economiza tempo e recursos, tornando o processo mais eficiente.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-24d3f58 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"24d3f58\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0c5e8a6 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0c5e8a6\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-reader-unique-id=\"12\"><strong>Maior reten\u00e7\u00e3o de clientes:<\/strong><\/p><p data-reader-unique-id=\"13\">O smarketing n\u00e3o se limita apenas a atrair novos clientes, mas tamb\u00e9m a manter os existentes. O marketing pode fornecer informa\u00e7\u00f5es \u00fateis para as equipes de vendas, permitindo que eles atendam melhor as necessidades dos clientes. Isso resulta em maior satisfa\u00e7\u00e3o e fidelidade do cliente.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-66da9be e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"66da9be\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d347855 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"d347855\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-reader-unique-id=\"14\"><strong>Melhora a comunica\u00e7\u00e3o:<\/strong><\/p><p data-reader-unique-id=\"15\">A comunica\u00e7\u00e3o aberta e eficaz entre marketing e vendas \u00e9 um dos pilares do smarketing. Isso leva a uma compreens\u00e3o mais profunda das metas e desafios de cada equipe, promovendo um ambiente de trabalho mais colaborativo e produtivo.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ca2f395 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"ca2f395\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-715324f elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"715324f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-reader-unique-id=\"18\"><strong>Melhoria da an\u00e1lise de dados:<\/strong><\/p><p data-reader-unique-id=\"19\">O compartilhamento de informa\u00e7\u00f5es e dados entre marketing e vendas oferece uma vis\u00e3o mais completa do desempenho. Isso permite ajustar estrat\u00e9gias com base em resultados reais e tomar decis\u00f5es mais informadas.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-af3d5d2 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"af3d5d2\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-7880186 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"7880186\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">6 Dicas para Implementar Smarketing nas Empresas<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-102239f e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"102239f\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-cd1405f elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"cd1405f\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-reader-unique-id=\"22\"><strong>1. Estabele\u00e7a metas compartilhadas<\/strong><\/p><p data-reader-unique-id=\"23\">O primeiro passo para o sucesso do smarketing \u00e9 estabelecer metas compartilhadas entre marketing e vendas. Essas metas devem ser espec\u00edficas, mensur\u00e1veis e alinhadas aos objetivos da empresa. Ter metas comuns ajuda a garantir que ambas as equipes trabalhem na mesma dire\u00e7\u00e3o<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8301a6d e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"8301a6d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-0c50533 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"0c50533\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-reader-unique-id=\"24\"><strong>2. Comunique-se regularmente<\/strong><\/p><p data-reader-unique-id=\"25\">A comunica\u00e7\u00e3o \u00e9 a espinha dorsal do smarketing. Promova reuni\u00f5es regulares entre as equipes de marketing e vendas para discutir o progresso, compartilhar informa\u00e7\u00f5es sobre leads e clientes, e alinhar estrat\u00e9gias. A tecnologia, como software de CRM (Customer Relationship Management), pode facilitar esse processo.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-3564bc5 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"3564bc5\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-5ab089e elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"5ab089e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-reader-unique-id=\"26\"><strong>3. Defina e refine os processos<\/strong><\/p><p data-reader-unique-id=\"27\">Desenvolva processos claros para a passagem de leads do marketing para as vendas. Isso inclui a defini\u00e7\u00e3o de crit\u00e9rios para leads qualificados, a cria\u00e7\u00e3o de conte\u00fado de suporte \u00e0s vendas e a automa\u00e7\u00e3o de fluxos de trabalho sempre que poss\u00edvel. \u00c0 medida que a empresa evolui, \u00e9 importante revisar e aprimorar continuamente esses processos.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-6fd3dd4 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"6fd3dd4\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-51e0e95 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"51e0e95\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-reader-unique-id=\"28\"><strong>4. Compartilhe dados e informa\u00e7\u00f5es<\/strong><\/p><p data-reader-unique-id=\"29\">O compartilhamento de dados \u00e9 crucial para o smarketing. O marketing deve fornecer informa\u00e7\u00f5es detalhadas sobre os leads, incluindo intera\u00e7\u00f5es e hist\u00f3rico de compras. As vendas devem, por sua vez, fornecer feedback sobre a qualidade dos leads e as necessidades dos clientes. Uma plataforma de CRM eficaz facilita o compartilhamento de dados.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8e9959b e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"8e9959b\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-dbf77c0 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"dbf77c0\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p data-reader-unique-id=\"30\"><strong>5. Treinamento e desenvolvimento conjunto<\/strong><\/p><p data-reader-unique-id=\"31\">Promova o treinamento conjunto entre marketing e vendas. Isso pode incluir sess\u00f5es de capacita\u00e7\u00e3o para garantir que ambas as equipes entendam as estrat\u00e9gias, os produtos e os clientes da empresa. O treinamento conjunto tamb\u00e9m ajuda a criar uma linguagem comum e a aumentar a compreens\u00e3o m\u00fatua.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-c7ed00d e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"c7ed00d\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bc4e967 elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"bc4e967\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h4 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Ferramentas para alinhar Marketing e Vendas\n<\/h4>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-8e6b157 e-flex e-con-boxed e-con e-parent\" data-id=\"8e6b157\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;boxed&quot;}\" data-core-v316-plus=\"true\">\n\t\t\t\t\t<div class=\"e-con-inner\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-b44bb48 elementor-widget__width-initial elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"b44b